categories: Category:Stormtrooper officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Arhul Crace was a lieutenant in the Stormtrooper Corps during the Galactic Civil War. Along with a squad of stormtroopers, he was sent to capture the leading members of the Osaji Syndicate and tracked them through Tirahnn and Centares, before confronting Osaji Hux on Muskree.
